Eating America with Anthony Anderson - Season 1, Episode 4




New Orleans Food Festival

Anthony Anderson pops up in the Big Easy to make his way through the New Orleans Wine and Food Experience and tries NOLA-inspired delights by over 70 restaurant vendors before going behind-the-scenes to cook with the elite competitors vying for the coveted title of "King of Louisiana Seafood."




Original Air Date: 18-Aug-2014
